metadata.name: Relentless LifeMap #1
metadata.description:
The Impact Theory Relentless LifeMap is a roadmap designed to guide you towards a life well-lived. The ideas expressed in this map will encourage you to explore a particular lifestyle, what the Japanese refer to as “kaizen” - the art of never-ending improvement. May these words allow you to change your Frame of Reference by encouraging you to believe that you can always improve and that by living your life in Relentless pursuit of skills that matter, you will find progress and meaning. 

[View Fullscreen](https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmQ88RwLUBmwBQeJFLrxMLigmyF1TXsu5PYqLWNJDNeTAH/1.html)
